    <div class="main">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-title">What is Mailchimp?</div><div class="prose"><p>Mailchimp is the world's most popular email marketing platform — used by 13 million businesses worldwide. It covers everything from simple newsletters to complex automated customer journeys, with a drag-and-drop builder that makes professional emails accessible to anyone with no design experience.</p><p>Its AI features include subject line optimisation that predicts open rates before you send, send-time optimisation that automatically delivers emails when each subscriber is most likely to open, and AI-generated email content suggestions. The Creative Assistant pulls your brand colours and fonts automatically from your website.</p><p>Mailchimp's free plan is the most generous in email marketing — up to 500 contacts and 1,000 sends per month, with access to templates, basic automations and audience analytics. For small businesses just starting with email, it's the obvious first choice.</p></div></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-title">Key Features</div><div class="features-grid"><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🤖</div><div class="feat-name">AI Subject Lines</div><div class="feat-desc">Predicts open rate performance before you send — A/B test AI-generated subject lines automatically.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">⏰</div><div class="feat-name">Send Time Optimisation</div><div class="feat-desc">AI delivers each email when that specific subscriber is most likely to open — improves open rates without any manual work.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🎨</div><div class="feat-name">Creative Assistant</div><div class="feat-desc">Automatically pulls your brand colours, fonts and logo from your website — branded emails in seconds.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🔄</div><div class="feat-name">Automations</div><div class="feat-desc">Pre-built automation journeys — welcome series, abandoned cart, re-engagement and birthday emails.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">📊</div><div class="feat-name">Audience Analytics</div><div class="feat-desc">Detailed reporting on opens, clicks, revenue and audience growth — with AI-powered insights on what to do next.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🔗</div><div class="feat-name">500+ Integrations</div><div class="feat-desc">Connects to Shopify, WooCommerce, Salesforce, Canva and 500+ other tools.</div></div></div></div>
      <div class="card">
